Date: 31st October 2025
Day: Friday

Dear Diary,
Today was a calm and pleasant day. I woke up early and went for a short walk. The weather was cool, and it felt refreshing. At school, we had a small Halloween celebration, and everyone dressed up in creative costumes. I spent some time with my friends and had a lot of fun. In the evening, I finished my homework and watched a movie with my family. Overall, it was a good and relaxing day.
